    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who have withdrawn or secluded themselves from the world for religious reasons. Examples are the recluses of the East in the early Christian centuries.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
